y Policy<\/h2><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a01c8d1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a01c8d1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5432b7a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5432b7a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-417fef0 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-heading\" data-id=\"417fef0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;slideInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:100}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" ><div class=\"ekit-heading elementskit-section-title-wraper text_left   ekit_heading_tablet-   ekit_heading_mobile-\"><h2 class=\"ekit-heading--title elementskit-section-title \">Privacy Policy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<div class='ekit-heading__description'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Shila Vive<\/strong> respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Information We Collect<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>We may collect:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Name, phone number, email address<\/p>\n<p>Shipping and billing address<\/p>\n<p>Payment transaction details (processed securely via Razorpay)<\/p>\n<p><strong>Use of Information<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Your information is used for:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Order processing and delivery<\/p>\n<p>Customer support<\/p>\n<p>Fraud prevention and transaction security<\/p>\n<p><strong>Sharing of Data<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>We may share customer information with:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Payment partners like Razorpay<\/p>\n<p>Courier and logistics partners<\/p>\n<p>Government authorities if required under applicable law<\/p>\n<p><strong>Data Security<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>We do not store card or payment instrument credentials, as required under Payment Aggregator Guidelines.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Marketing Communication<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>By using our services, you may receive updates through SMS, Email, or WhatsApp. You may opt out anytime.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy Privacy Policy Shila Vive respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. Information We Collect<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-9055","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9055","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9055"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9055\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9059,"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/9055\/revisions\/9059"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.shilavive.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9055"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}